Package: PMC
Type: Package
Title: The Peat Moisture Code
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person("Sophie", "Wilkinson", , "sophie_wilkinson@sfu.ca", role = c("aut", "cre"), 
    comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-4043-6277"))
Maintainer: The package maintainer <yourself@somewhere.net>
Description: 
    The PMC incorporates peatland hydrological research to model the 
    change in storage in the peatland water balance in a simple to use bookkeeping approach, akin to that used for the Drought Code and the Duff Moisture Code.
